). Papillae anales weakly covered with setae. Elongate antevaginal lamella strongly wrinkled and sclerotized. Apophysis posterioris slender and longer than apophysis anterioris. Ductus bursae broad, waved, membranous, with short spines partly. Corpus bursae ovoid, membranous, with a bundle of diverse sized spines in medial area of bursae.
